Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.87,0:00:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之真名为晓之圣龙骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.87,0:00:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(496,438)\fs21}Burning Fighting Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在与邪龙族的宿命之战中无所畏惧的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(261,438)\fs21}Wyvern
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.69,0:00:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在现世的名字是 季堂锐太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂寄于此身的龙骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.17,0:00:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——OP——
